<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <div class="container" style="margin-top: 30px">

  </div>
</head>

<style>
  .bb {
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
<body>
<div class="container" style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 35px">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Korisnik info - <span style="color: #A9CC2D; ">Veeam Cloud Connect</span></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="container" style="margin-top: 30px">
    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "logomail.png", width:"400px",style: "padding-top: 18px;" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Informacije o korisniku koji se registrirao na stranicu </h3><h2><%= link_to "cc.megatrend.com" , "http://cc.megatrend.com/hr" %></h2>
  <br>
  <h3>Informacije o korisniku su: </h3><br>
  <div class="container" >
    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Ime: <span class="bb"><%= @user.first_name%></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Prezime: <span class="bb"><%= @user.last_name%></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Ime tvrtke: <span class="bb"><%= @user.company %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>OIB: <span class="bb"><%= @user.cin %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>e-mail: <span class="bb"><%= @user.email %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Tel. broj: <span class="bb"><%= @user.phone %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Država: <span class="bb"><%= @user.country %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Grad: <span class="bb"><%= @user.city %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row" >
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Poštanski broj: <span class="bb"><%= @user.postal_code %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="well">
          <h4>Adresa: <span class="bb"><%= @user.address %></span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <hr>
  <h4  style="margin-top: 10px"><span style="color: #A9CC2D; ">Veeam Cloud Connect</span> - postanite <span style="color: #A9CC2D; ">„Always On”</span> tvrtka!</h4>
  <br/>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-2">
      <small>Ako ste ovu poruku primili greškom ili vam nije namijenjena, ne koristite ju, ne kopirajte, ne distribuirajte, ne otvarajte privitke, odmah ju obrišite sa svog računalnog sustava i obavijestite pošiljatelja da ste to napravili. Hvala!</small>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>